Shattering		KEY:SHATTER		TYPE:Weapon.Melee.Ranged	PLUS:2	VISIBLE:QUALIFY	SOURCEPAGE:p.28	PRETYPE:1,Enhancement	PRETYPE:2,Weapon,Melee,Ranged	SPROP:Deals an extra 2d6 points of damage against inanimate objects and crystalline creatures, explodes with a crash on critical hit, dealing an extra 1d10 points of damage to objects and crystalline creatures on a successful critical hit. If the weapon's critical multiplier is x3, it deals an extra 2d10 points of damage instead, and if the multiplier is x4, it deals an extra 3d10 points instead. Ignores the hardness of objects with a hardness of 10 or lower.
